    SVMData is a program designed to create appropriate input data for the RankSVM algorithm that involves Pairwise Classification. Specifically, instead of working in the space of query-document vectors, e.g. x1, x2, x3, we transform them into a new space in which a pair of documents is represented as the difference between their feature vectors.
